{"tid":1453943,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"警方扮示威者 自導自演 一齊去yahoo tv新聞散播出去","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T05:56:36.000Z","uid":160147,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a8aec986d2154c304160340df059e793b41b4d06","tid":1453943,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6UrHmiu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6UrHmiu.png&h=fb01f7ac&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一個目標：對付警察 <br />\n因為警察冇一個係無辜架<br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n藍絲永遠唔明示威意義 唔好同佢地explain啦</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n得閑就幫下手  唔好俾警察瞞騙藍絲市民！<br />\n1 留comment<br />\n2 like 同路人comment<br />\n<br />\n唔知幾時開始扮示威者？ 尋日先扮 定6月有扮？<br />\n<br />\n拉普通示威者 立唔到功 <br />\n但拉縱火示威者 就係立大功<br />\n有人煽動放火 會唔會幫警升職？<br />\n<br />\n保皇黨話背後有人策劃。 係邊個策劃呢？<br />\n<br />\n藍絲經常問：「點解今次示威特別暴力 以前較和平？ 」<br />\n同警察有冇關呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.tv.yahoo.com/hknewsvideo/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%88%BB%E6%84%8F%E4%BB%A5%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%89%93%E6%89%AE%E6%96%B9%E4%BE%BF%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95-161341536.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.tv.yahoo.com%2Fhknewsvideo%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E5%2588%25BB%25E6%2584%258F%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2589%25AE%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595-161341536.html&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=3fe77d14\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.tv.yahoo.com/hknewsvideo/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%88%BB%E6%84%8F%E4%BB%A5%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%89%93%E6%89%AE%E6%96%B9%E4%BE%BF%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95-161341536.html</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果開yahoo account好難 你可以放